{"tid":204329,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"時代的眼淚！戶田惠梨香和「夜神月」藤原龍也睽違 11 年再接吻！","createTime":"2017-04-17T03:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T14:38:25.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07ec4dcb0c95cee07574c032831d8b49753e6a9c","tid":204329,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64808/58f2ef219b1fe.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64808%2F58f2ef219b1fe.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=9e92747b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由大場鶇原作、小畑健作畫的日本超人氣漫畫《死亡筆記本》改編成動畫、電視劇、電影都獲得許多觀眾的支持，尤其是 2006 年上映的電影版，由藤原龍也飾演主角「夜神月」、松山研一飾演「L」、戶田惠梨香飾演「彌海砂」的演員組合，被許多《死亡筆記本》粉絲奉為最成功的真人化，而現在那一對《死亡筆記本》情侶黨暌違 11 年，終於再度一起演出愛情戲！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64808/58f2ef2282565.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64808%2F58f2ef2282565.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=b2dda9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藤原龍也和戶田惠梨香在最新的日劇《反轉》中共同主演，這部日劇是改編自知名作家湊佳苗的同名小說，藤原龍也和戶田惠梨香在劇中飾演情侶深瀨和久以及美穗子，男女主角在幸福交往之後，美穗子有一天卻突然收到Baby被黑「暴牙舊照」流出！超寬下顎超驚人一封信時起了變化，上面寫著田北辰反對迪士尼擴建：「深瀨和久是殺人兇手！」，開啟懸疑劇情。<br />\n<br />\n▼不過最讓粉絲激動的是，藤原龍也和戶田惠梨香在第一集就甜蜜接吻，瞬間讓人有彌海砂和夜神月婚後生活的既視感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64808/58f2eeea1f187.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64808%2F58f2eeea1f187.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=63701424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼在 11 年前的《死亡筆記本》電影版中，瘋狂迷戀著夜神月的彌海砂，熱情獻上自己的香吻，可是羨煞了多少彌海砂的粉絲，畢竟戶田惠梨香當年可是紅遍亞洲的美少女。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64808/58f2eeeae8760.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64808%2F58f2eeeae8760.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=3f3d2a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了這一對《死亡筆記本》情侶再聚首，湊佳苗的推理懸疑小說改編成戲劇後也一向廣受好評，讓《反轉》成為了極受觀眾期待的新檔日劇，身為彌海砂和夜神月 CP 檔的各位能夠不追嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64808/58f2ef2361f11.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64808%2F58f2ef2361f11.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=3725650b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce778ff80b75e06ac2a78ca137eb0e0b5b822d8f","tid":204329,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:19:37.000Z","msg":"肥咗靚返曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970eac3051d95bf88ce8dc28550a944deaa04ff3","tid":204329,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:20:35.000Z","msg":"戶田真係好撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有姐姐FEEL"},{"pid":"b0b50e0a9f95a681654d53974c36c93f876988b9","tid":204329,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"美穗子有一天卻突然<span style=\"color: red;\">收到Baby被黑「暴牙舊照」流出！超寬下顎超驚人一封信時起了變化，上面寫著田北辰反對迪士尼擴建</span>：「深瀨和久是殺人兇手！」，開啟懸疑劇情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7411681a1a29012a2c4b301613f0b9b8bcad249e","tid":204329,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"戶田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3b3c8f17e3f1003a61920cb13edb1879ec72dd","tid":204329,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美穗子有一天卻突然<span style=\"color: red;\">收到Baby被黑「暴牙舊照」流出！超寬下顎超驚人一封信時起了變化，上面寫著田北辰反對迪士尼擴建</s